\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 Methods\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 Study Design and Ethics\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 This cross-sectional clinical study was conducted between April 2023 and March 2024 at a university-affiliated research center. The study protocol was approved by the institutional ethics committee, and all participants provided written informed consent prior to participation.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs28 \cf0 Participants\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 A total of 310 adults aged 18\'9635 years were recruited through university campuses, social media advertisements, and community outreach programs. Inclusion criteria included ownership and regular use of a smartphone for at least two years. Exclusion criteria included diagnosed sleep disorders, diabetes mellitus, cardiovascular disease, chronic inflammatory conditions, pregnancy, night-shift work, and use of medications affecting sleep or metabolism.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

