\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Smartphone use was assessed using a combination of self-reported questionnaires and device-generated usage logs when available. Participants reported average daily smartphone use over the preceding three months, including total screen time and usage during the two hours before bedtime.\
