\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 Data were collected on physical activity, dietary habits, alcohol consumption, smoking status, perceived stress, and socioeconomic status. These variables were included as covariates in statistical analyses.\
